    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/cea1399ebfa4fd0e3d7e9ad3212c842c.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d983ad6abbc814d43a4d625195bdfc47.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d983ad6abbc814d43a4d625195bdfc47.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d983ad6abbc814d43a4d625195bdfc47.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/3a7c44ff68afbfd2ff36bb5cfebf6adb.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极速。狂烈。无阻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入《Rivals Hover League》，这项风靡全宇宙的正式载具格斗运动正等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为驾驶员，你需要驾驶悬浮载具，主宰整个竞技场，与队伍共同成长，最终铸就传奇。<br>智胜你的对手。娴熟地悬浮，加速，射击，拿下 MVP 殊荣吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/daf78b6a0c85540a481699cbd3528da2.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/daf78b6a0c85540a481699cbd3528da2.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/daf78b6a0c85540a481699cbd3528da2.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/1bb53e2e3eb5d275a01c039b5d6b240c.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘却地面的束缚吧。在此处，运动永无止境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控你的悬浮载具，在竞技场中自由滑行、漂移、轰炸，并借助反重力推进、高空跳跃与精准制动，一路所向披靡。<br>每辆载具都如同真实机械，其重量、摩擦力与碰撞冲击力皆真实可感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次射击、每次转向、每一分、每一秒， 一切皆在你的掌控之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d39e301b9d05a322c122be65df7e77ba.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d39e301b9d05a322c122be65df7e77ba.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/d39e301b9d05a322c122be65df7e77ba.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/12de89f9e74f41b902dc2ccdcfc98db9.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建一支最多四人的队伍并加入联赛。<br>单打独斗当然可以，但胜利需要团队协作。<br>与队友默契配合，锁定敌方目标，携手在混乱中奋勇突围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲入竞技场，拿下胜利吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/048224fdbd1cb95ce5e674263d6bdc5d.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/048224fdbd1cb95ce5e674263d6bdc5d.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/048224fdbd1cb95ce5e674263d6bdc5d.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/56176ea069d09fab7a91de664ef90eb8.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以速度优势穿透对手防线，<br>用强大火力为队友筑起护盾，<br>或凭借战术科技扰乱场上局势。<br><br>挑选各具特色的悬浮载具，每一类在战斗中都拥有独特的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据情况选择正确的载具，胜利的天平已经向你倾斜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/1919109490047b42e37faa4c0544c549.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/1919109490047b42e37faa4c0544c549.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/1919109490047b42e37faa4c0544c549.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/40157e53b6d0fd40d167a7f5bb66a16f.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Rivals Hover League》中，胜利方式不止一种。<br>每场比赛都有不同的规则、目标和场地。随之而来的，是全新的策略以及不断变化的团队打法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迅速适应，机智应对，将每场游戏都转化为独属于你的胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/4cff8999e2ef3d79c93e790df2567037.poster.avif?t=1770609979\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/4cff8999e2ef3d79c93e790df2567037.webm?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/4cff8999e2ef3d79c93e790df2567037.mp4?t=1770609979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251280/extras/b176a155a97954d495f3986e457c849f.webp?t=1770609979\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即加入愿望单，并加入我们的官方 Discord！<br>与开发者畅快交流，在驾驶员锦标赛中展现实力，并与社区伙伴携手，共同塑造 RHL 的未来！<br><br>与我们一起逐步打造 RHL 吧！</p>",
